	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=409709><span id= >Swollboulder</span></a><br><span id=notbold>1 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I had to learn to make these pretty quick as this item is required to make some of the lower trivial tailoring items, i.e. cured silk mask.&nbsp;&nbsp;I found the easiest place to do this was in <b>East Freeport</b>.  I purchased both the Packet of Kiola Sap and the Bottles from the NPC named <b>Sun Alemaker</b>.  The Packet of Kiola Sap cost me .115 pp each and the Bottles went for .005 pp each.  The Water Flask is available right around the corner from the NPC <b>Innkeep Hunter</b> in the East Freeport Inn building (building with the Soulbinder out front) for .010 pp each.  The nice thing about making this in Freeport is that both buildings have a brew barrel very close by.<br><br>Please note the Bottle is refunded on failure.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Sep 17 00:22:28 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
